> assistant
Done — the React app was created at:

```bash
./react-bun-example
```

It includes:

- React 19
- Vite
- Bun lockfile / Bun-managed dependencies
- Tailwind CSS v4
- `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin
- Minimal Tailwind-styled `App.jsx`

Start it with:

```bash
cd react-bun-example
bun dev
```

Then open the local URL Vite prints, usually:

```text
http://localhost:5173
```


